title: Times the Duggars Reminded Us That God Comes First in Their Family
text:
Times the Duggars Reminded Us That God Comes First in Their Family Tanvier Peart 
duggarfam/Instagram 
The Duggar family is notorious for many things. They're a clan of many people -- including tons of brothers, sisters, aunts, uncles, nieces, nephews, and cousins. They're a family who documents parts of their lives in front of the camera for all to see. And another thing the Duggar family is notorious for is being a family that holds their faith very close to their hearts. 
Here's a look at a few moments that prove the Duggars are all about their Christian faith, no matter what.
